      "content": "honestly he's like 75 and he's really insistent that he just needs to lie down. he's saying he feels fine otherwise, just \"foggy\" from the jet lag. if it's just travel fatigue or maybe some dehydration, can we just give him some water and maybe an aspirin and let him sleep for a few hours to see if it passes? i'd rather not panic and call an ambulance if it's just the flight catching up to him.",
