      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it feels like a lot of an overreaction for someone who just flew 14 hours. he's actually kinda laughing it off now, just saying he's \"clumsy\" because he's tired. if we wait just two or three hours to see if some rest and hydration fixes the \"fogginess\" and the tingling, would that be okay? what's the actual worst case if it really is just exhaustion?",
